{{Quote|This thing has sixty-five pockets &ndash; most of them hidden. I haven't even opened half of them yet.|An owner of the belt|<ref name="Agents of Deception">{{SWGTCG|set=Agents of Deception|cardname=Belt of Bodo Baas}}</ref>}}
The '''Belt of Master Bodo Baas''' was an article of clothing first found by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Bodo Baas]]. In the centuries after Baas' demise the belt was passed down through various members of the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]]. The last Jedi to own the belt was Jedi Master [[Ashka Boda]], who was also in possession of [[Tedryn Holocron|Master Baas' holocron]]. It is not known what happened to the belt when Boda was captured by [[Imperial Sentinel]]s and killed by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. It later resurfaced after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].<ref name="SWG">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=item|Belt of Master Bodo Baas}}</ref>

{{Clothes-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Belt of Master Bodo Baas is an item in ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', first introduced in Chapter 7. To obtain the item, the player has to collect several Jedi artifacts. It boosts several stats of the player character and, when worn in combination with a [[Jedi apparel/Legends|Jedi robe]], gives skill bonuses to [[Lightsaber/Legends|Lightsaber]] assembly and Lightsaber experimentation.

